_sText:
This is my entry for the FPSB Marble Tracks contest. It is meant to be used in Counter-Strike:Source. 
To install just extract the bsp file included in the RAR file into your "maps" folder.

I know, it lacks a video but I seriously don't have time for that. Also the screens are not that good either since the map is huge. Please download and try it.

Enjoy!
